The '''''Wendiri Nightstar''''' was a luxury pleasure cruiser that was attacked by [[Warlord/Legends|Warlord]] [[Delurin]]'s flagship, the ''[[Galaxy Dragon]]''. Though he managed to knock out the [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]] engines, a group of passengers were able to hold back his [[Dragon trooper (Bormterran)|dragon troopers]] long enough for them to be repaired, and the ship jumped into [[Lightspeed/Legends|lightspeed]] to escape.

